# Standard Refund Policy

1. Eligibility: Customers are eligible for a full refund within 30 days of purchase if the product is in its original packaging.
2. Digital Goods: Digital products are non-refundable once the download link has been accessed or the license key activated.
3. Processing Time: Once approved, refunds take 5-10 business days to appear on the original payment method.
4. Promotional Items: Items purchased as part of a "Buy One Get One" deal are only eligible for store credit unless the entire set is returned.
5. Exceptions: Personalized or custom-made items are strictly non-refundable under any circumstances.
6. Support: For further questions, please contact billing@agentos.ai or call 1-800-AGENTOS.
